    "Audience": "AZOA.Client"
  },
  "AdminBootstrap": {
    "__comment": "H2 operator:admin bootstrap (Services/Admin/AGENTS.md). BOTH SeedEmail and SeedSecret must be set (via env vars, e.g. AdminBootstrap__SeedEmail / AdminBootstrap__SeedSecret) for the seam to activate — either alone is inert. Empty by default: fail-closed, off until an operator deliberately arms it.",
