  "Quest": {
    "__comment": "Marketplace run-start quota (Managers/AGENTS.md §quest-run-quota). MaxRunsPerAvatarPerQuest caps a NON-owner's concurrent non-terminal runs of one quest (treasury/runner-drain guard); <=0 disables. OwnerLimitMultiplier scales the ceiling for the owner running their OWN quest; <=0 exempts the owner.",
