      "GuardianSets": {
        "__comment": "Config-driven Wormhole Guardian sets consumed by Secp256k1VaaSignatureVerifier. Key = Guardian-set index (string, the VAA header GuardianSetIndex). Value = ORDERED list of 0x-prefixed 20-byte Ethereum-style Guardian addresses; list position == Guardian index. INTENTIONALLY NO testnet/mainnet entries here: an absent set fails closed (no VAA can be verified — see Secp256k1VaaSignatureVerifier). Do NOT add placeholder/guessed addresses. Real testnet/mainnet sets must be supplied + independently verified per the per-environment procedure in conductor/tracks/api-safety-hardening/GUARDIAN-SET-SETUP.md, dropped into the matching appsettings.<Environment>.json under this same Blockchain:Wormhole:GuardianSets key. appsettings.Development.json carries the verified devnet (tilt) set, index 0."
      }
    },
